@apiHost = http://localhost:5208
@petshopApiHost = http://localhost:5218
@accessToken = paste-token-here
@cartId = 1
@reservationId = paste-reservation-id-here
@checkoutProductId = paste-checkout-product-id-here
@transactionId = 1
@paymentId = 9001

# 使用前請先啟動 PetShop compose:
# docker compose -f compose/petshop.api-dev.compose.yaml up --build
#
# 若要先重建乾淨資料庫:
# docker compose -f compose/petshop.api-dev.compose.yaml down -v
# docker compose -f compose/petshop.api-dev.compose.yaml up --build
#
# 建議順序:
# authorize -> token -> products -> services -> availability -> create hold
# -> create cart -> add reservation product -> add normal product -> estimate
# -> checkout create -> checkout complete -> get reservation
#
# 範例預期:
# grooming-basic 預約 2000 + pet-food-premium 1500 - 預約購買滿額折扣 100 = 3400

### OAuth authorize (從 Location header 取出 code)
POST {{apiHost}}/oauth/authorize
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

name=petshop-local-user&password=ignored&client_id=local-http&redirect_uri=https://localhost/callback&state=petshop

### OAuth token exchange
POST {{apiHost}}/oauth/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

code=paste-oauth-code-here

### 讀取標準商品目錄
GET {{apiHost}}/api/products

### 讀取 PetShop 美容服務目錄
GET {{petshopApiHost}}/petshop-api/services

### 查詢可預約 slot
GET {{petshopApiHost}}/petshop-api/availability?serviceId=grooming-basic&date=2026-05-01

### 建立 reservation hold
POST {{petshopApiHost}}/petshop-api/reservations/holds
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serviceId": "grooming-basic",
  "startAt": "2026-05-01T02:00:00Z",
  "venueId": "room-a",
  "staffId": "staff-amy"
}

### 查詢目前會員 reservations
GET {{petshopApiHost}}/petshop-api/reservations
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 查詢單筆 reservation
GET {{petshopApiHost}}/petshop-api/reservations/{{reservationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 建立購物車
POST {{apiHost}}/api/carts/create
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 加入預約對應 hidden product
POST {{apiHost}}/api/carts/{{cartId}}/items
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "{{checkoutProductId}}",
  "qty": 1
}

### 加入一般商品，觸發預約購買滿額折扣
POST {{apiHost}}/api/carts/{{cartId}}/items
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "pet-food-premium",
  "qty": 1
}

### 試算 PetShop 預約購買滿額折扣
POST {{apiHost}}/api/carts/{{cartId}}/estimate
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 建立 checkout transaction
POST {{apiHost}}/api/checkout/create
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cartId": {{cartId}}
}

### 完成 checkout，預期會確認 reservation 並輸出 PetShop PoC notification log
POST {{apiHost}}/api/checkout/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": {{transactionId}},
  "paymentId": {{paymentId}},
  "satisfaction": 5,
  "shopComments": "PetShop local smoke test"
}

### checkout 後重新查詢 reservation，預期 status = confirmed
GET {{petshopApiHost}}/petshop-api/reservations/{{reservationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### checkout 前取消 hold (獨立情境使用，不要在 checkout 後執行)
POST {{petshopApiHost}}/petshop-api/reservations/{{reservationId}}/cancel-hold
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
